      "id": "product-429",
      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "PD Ostrich Show Farm"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "PD Ostrich Show Farm is a top attraction in Port Dickson, with ostriches as the star but there are lots of other farm and pet animals, including rabbits, ponies, donkeys, birds, snakes.The farm offers guided tours that take visitors through the various stages of ostrich breeding and farming. Visitors can learn about the different types of ostriches, their characteristics, and their life cycle. There are also opportunities to feed and pet the ostriches, as well as take photos with them.Apart from ostriches, the farm also features other farm animals such as rabbits, goats, and horses. There are various shows and activities available for visitors, including ostrich races, egg painting demonstrations, and a bird show featuring different species of birds."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Petting farm with ostriches, rabbits and other pets & farm animals. Lots of fruit trees"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Planet Jurassic is a dinosaur park with some sculptures which can also move and sound."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Planet Jurassic is a dinosaur park included in this combo package are Carnivorous Plant Garden and The Country Cat Cafe"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "PD Ostrich reserves the right to substitute Train Safari with Horse Carriage ride in the event the train is not available"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "PD Ostrich Show Farm is a fun and educational destination for families and animal lovers. The farm is open daily from 9 am to 6 pm, and admission fees vary depending on age and nationality. Visitors can also purchase souvenirs and ostrich-related products at the farm's gift shop."
              }
            ]
